        "text": "ye have",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", etc.) Pilate gives the guards quickly: and yet, as it were with indignation (cf. ch. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Matthew 28:11-12",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "), dismisses the calumniators quickly also.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "br",
